<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">The Lamb of God</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Mar 27, 2017 00:00</p>
</header> <div class="org-center">

 <figure id="orgb12cad6"> <img src="../images/posts/20170327-lamb.jpg" alt="20170327-lamb.jpg" width="100%"></img></figure></div>

 <p>
(Painting:  <i>Lamb</i> by Francisco Zurbarán) <sup> <a id="fnr.1" class="footref" href="#fn.1" role="doc-backlink">1</a></sup></p>

 <p>
The sounds of Passover <br></br>
fill the streets with <br></br>
desperate bleating <br></br>
as all the animals <br></br>
must be dragged <br></br>
to play their <br></br>
sacrificial roles.
</p>

 <p>
All, that is, save one <br></br>
who goes quietly <br></br>
with determination, <br></br>
strength, and purpose.
</p>

 <p>
Lamb of God <br></br>
have mercy on me.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>

 <div class="tagline" id="org6527956">
